  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span>CSDN</span> <span>2026-04-07 17:31</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">江苏</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2bea1434&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FS1iaf4GgGjEze0htvKakUUYCiaIkx5pt7gUXP96gVDrg36H1GK9RrKS0moxnP0HMLvpDnqiafB2FicxfMCK2MGS3IJUHNeCdPo56lMqCDLPajsQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>当 AI 真正进入产业齿轮，如何跨越落地的“最后一公里”？</p>\n  <p data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;text-align: center;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 43 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/Pn4Sm0RsAujqPrtpN5QqqOuSG0AdUUx8wRg3vvr7aQJicdC0cHDBqZrJBZajQUXx97BwNaAE6L6x7OGlsTIpWjw/0?wx_fmt=gif\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"230\" data-imgfileid=\"100251368\" data-ratio=\"0.125\" style=\"width: 578px;height: 230px;\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7846b646&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FPn4Sm0RsAujqPrtpN5QqqOuSG0AdUUx8wRg3vvr7aQJicdC0cHDBqZrJBZajQUXx97BwNaAE6L6x7OGlsTIpWjw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></span></p>\n  <p data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;text-align: left;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 43 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">责编 | 梦依丹</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: normal;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">出品 | CSDN（ID：CSDNnews）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">当下，把 AI 嵌入业务并不难，甚至很容易，但让它在真实的业务里扛住压力、稳定跑通、才是最硬核的考验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在搜索、医疗、零售、办公、工业等垂直领域，大模型的落地正面临着多重“硬约束”：如何消除金融决策中的逻辑幻觉？如何内化医疗专家沉淀几十年的隐性经验？如何平衡万亿级流量下的算力成本与响应速度？这些问题无法在标准化的基座模型中找到现成答案，只能在真实的业务战场上通过精密的工程化手段逐一攻克。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果说过去两年的关键词是“大模型+”，那么 2026 年的核心命题无疑是“业务深耕”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">4 月 17-18 日，由 CSDN 与奇点智能研究院联合举办的「<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">2026 奇点智能技术大会</span>」将在上海·环球港凯悦酒店召开。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在「AI+行业落地实践」专题中，我们邀请了来自小红书、京东、蚂蚁、平安、百度、金山办公、中能拾贝的 7 位实战派专家，深度复盘他们在万亿级流量、强专业壁垒场景下的破局方案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100345898\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=83d358e1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FS1iaf4GgGjEx3usmibuGH7SjgfUO2Z8H7ibqOzNIoJzwqRcbupsqM2jnRfVrOIQRZNxFxOXicyPjyuIeVIUXHF0L8OMSmo8XhX0icibOXsWsCXNFY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11428571428571428\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"700\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100252192\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e2c5b48b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FPn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06QuwjkSP1G6wEJHaJCLTONqlcQexqRgJcIICxofIOJs6B6tWBfibb7now%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">社交与电商：从预测驱动转向“因果决策”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在海量用户交互的社交与电商领域，AI 不再只是搜索框，而是具备决策能力的 Agent。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">自适应强化学习驱动 AI 搜索 Agent 对齐在小红书的实践</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🔹 演讲嘉宾：陆承镪，小红书 AI 搜索生成算法负责人</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🤔 为什么值得听：搜索 Agent 需要在准确性、安全性与丰富度间动态平衡。陆承镪将现场分享小红书 SearchLLM Agent 的 RL 实践。他将分享如何通过自适应课程学习框架实现“因材施训”，在亿级搜索流量中实现多目标优化。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🎯 核心收益：掌握基于 GRPO 与门控聚合的多维奖励体系，解决 Agent 在训</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">练过程中的数据边际贡献递减问题。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">Agentic Commerce：商业世界模型中的因果建模实践</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🔹 演讲嘉宾：邓金秋，京东定价算法负责人，前 Uber/Bloomberg 算法专家</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🤔 为什么值得听：真正的商业挑战并非构建 Agent，而是刻画“决策—环境—结果”的因果关系。邓金秋将介绍 Agentic Commerce 框架，分享如何利用大模型语义先验结合因果方法，从传统预测迈向反事实推理。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🎯 核心收益：学习如何构建能够估计价格变化需求响应的“商业世界模型”，实现从预测到智能决策的跃迁。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11428571428571428\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"700\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100252191\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c0d6be04&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FPn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06QDyP5HTUOXsPlJWd79yygiasaqXicpN7ibIfqiak5WFpaxE1mGxxpfmMjiaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">金融与工业：构</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">建商业世界的“数字雷达</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当大模型面对数十亿量级的复杂企业数据与严苛的工业标准，工程化能力是唯一的入场券。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">基于世界模型与智能体的企业认知与动态评价体系</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🔹 演讲嘉宾：马宇翔，蚂蚁集团企业信用部算法负责人</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🤔 为什么值得听：在芝麻企业助手中，面对数十亿量级的复杂结构数据，如何保证响应快且结果准？马宇翔将分享在行业研究场景下，商业世界模型与 Agent 的研发应用经验，拆解如何构建企业认知的“数字雷达”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">工业智能跃迁：数据与知识驱动的工业场景 AI 工程化实践</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🔹 演讲嘉宾：</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">刘勇，中能拾贝创始人兼 CTO，深耕工业智能化 20 余年</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">🤔 为什么值得听：工业场景对确定性的要求近乎严苛。刘勇将分享拾贝工业智能操作系统的构建逻辑，解析数据与行业知识双驱动下的 AI 工程化路径，为“新质生产力”在电力等标杆行业的落地提供范式。</span></p>\n  <p styl